
** Global

- *C-x C-j* dired-jump


** Keys

- *w* dired-copy-filename-as-kill
- *U* dired-unmark-all-marks
- *M-{* dired-prev-marked-file
- *M-}* dired-next-marked-file

- *C-x C-q* wdired


** using of " * "

The marked files can be used in a dired shell command by a
whitespace surrounded asterix. To nullify this use =*""=.

  <example>
  '! echo * '
  '! echo *""'
  </example>
